# Title: MSSQL XPCmdshell Suspicious Execution
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-07-12
# Level: high
# Description: Detects when the MSSQL "xp_cmdshell" stored procedure is used to execute commands
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/application/mssqlserver/win_mssql_xp_cmdshell_audit_log.yml

Data="*object_name:xp_cmdshell*" Data="*statement:EXEC*" EventID=33205 Provider_Name="*MSSQL*"